-- Intesa Sanpaolo Chief Passera Backs EU's Proposal for Deposit Guarantees
-- Sonia Sirletti
-- 2010-07-13T10:47:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/intesa-sanpaolo-chief-passera-backs-eu-s-proposal-for-deposit-guarantees.html

          
          
             Intesa Chief Executive Officer
Corrardo Passera told reporters today in Milan that he backs the
European Union proposal for deposit guarantees.  
 Passera also said he’s ready to discuss UniCredit SpA CEO
Alessandro Profumo’s proposal to create a recovery fund and that
he’s skeptical about a possible banks rescue fund.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
